"Menu:\n"
"Set the key signature or insert a change of key signature\n"
"Sharpen or flatten a key signature or\n"
"hide it on printing"
msgstr ""
"Meny:\n"
"Ange tonart eller infoga en ändring av tonart\n"
"Skärpa eller platta till en tonartssignatur eller\n"
"dölja den vid utskrift"

