msgid "Spacing for Staff Group"
msgstr "Avstånd för notsystemgrupp"

#: ../actions/menus/ObjectMenu/Score/Typesetter/PrintLayout/VerticalSpacing/Staff-Spacing/StaffToStaffSpacing.scm:5
